  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      529.49,
      543.77,
      576.25
    ],
    "text": "The grouse of the petitioners had been that they had applied for the post of Grama Niladhari Grade II and had sat for a written exam and although they claim that they had obtained high marks, they have not been recruited.",
